headline: Allstate Wuerffel Trophy announces 2025 finalists for college football's top community service award
summary: ATLANTA, November 25, 2025--The Allstate Wuerffel Trophy today announced its 2025 finalists, recognizing three NCAA Football Bowl Subdivision (FBS) players who exemplify character, leadership and a deep commitment to serving others.
